  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/df35203b82e15cac5b5bd8f68d69da84.webp?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/53fa28c76a941b8d15c1b47de188d2eb.poster.avif?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/53fa28c76a941b8d15c1b47de188d2eb.webm?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/53fa28c76a941b8d15c1b47de188d2eb.mp4?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Chronocide: A physics-driven game where you defend the portal with traps and weapons.</strong> <br> <br>Chronocide brings a horde of undead for you and your friends to shoot, burn, crush, throw, impale, poison, freeze and hurt in other imaginative ways. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grind your enemies down on their way to the temporal portals with cleverly placed traps and your weapons. Save civilization from being wiped out while you're at it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn up to 5 stars per level, each grade rewards more points to use for acquiring items or upgrading your hero, traps and weapons. Every hero can acquire traps/weapons that are either neutral or specific for them.  <br><br>The campaign can be played in solo or co-op mode (up to 4 players). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game is meant to be <u>challenging</u>.</strong> If at first you don't succeed at a level, try, try again. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or switch to casual difficulty (and earn less stars if you complete the level). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missing stars on a level? Replay it to increase your rewards.  <br> <br>Original soundtrack by <strong>Malin Eriksson</strong>. <br>    <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/b69f3e821abf8d027be770fffeef2699.webp?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/2f5d70c1a79eff5d1564b1be19ae3c82.poster.avif?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/2f5d70c1a79eff5d1564b1be19ae3c82.webm?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/2f5d70c1a79eff5d1564b1be19ae3c82.mp4?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>TL;DR</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Footage, content and gameplay is subject to change at any time during the early access period.  <br> <br>During early access, content will be released continuously until the 3 acts that wraps up the main story are complete.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every act consists of 8 levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number of traps, weapons, enemy types and levels will increase with time. <br><br><u><strong>NOTE: Only 1 act is available so far in the early access.</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This will change further along development. <br><br>Also, there will be <strong>bugs</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hopefully, any such arising will be easy to find and get rid of with the help of the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/70970c2052064d4af0bd502490cd58c5.webp?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/d1d231264a1f43eb35a364c2906cf297.poster.avif?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/d1d231264a1f43eb35a364c2906cf297.webm?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/d1d231264a1f43eb35a364c2906cf297.mp4?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The base game will contain the first 3 acts which is the main story arc. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the acts, more traps, weapons and other items will be available. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through the campaign to unlock more game modes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 4 available heroes play very differently and complement eachother; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Waldis the wizard - expert in elemental damage, using mostly projectile weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Rolanda the paladin - employs buffs/debuffs and uses (mostly) melee weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Mike the soldier - uses instant-hit bullet weapons that require mana to reload. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Anthia the necromancer - inflicts spell damage instead of wielding weapons, also has access to minions. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/a196b13d2934ba1da5ab3e8aaade3e13.webp?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the official Discord server if you have any feedback about the game or the balancing thereof.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/df35203b82e15cac5b5bd8f68d69da84.webp?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/53fa28c76a941b8d15c1b47de188d2eb.poster.avif?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/53fa28c76a941b8d15c1b47de188d2eb.webm?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/53fa28c76a941b8d15c1b47de188d2eb.mp4?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Chronocide: A physics-driven game where you defend the portal with traps and weapons.</strong> <br> <br>Chronocide brings a horde of undead for you and your friends to shoot, burn, crush, throw, impale, poison, freeze and hurt in other imaginative ways. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grind your enemies down on their way to the temporal portals with cleverly placed traps and your weapons. Save civilization from being wiped out while you're at it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn up to 5 stars per level, each grade rewards more points to use for acquiring items or upgrading your hero, traps and weapons. Every hero can acquire traps/weapons that are either neutral or specific for them.  <br><br>The campaign can be played in solo or co-op mode (up to 4 players). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game is meant to be <u>challenging</u>.</strong> If at first you don't succeed at a level, try, try again. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or switch to casual difficulty (and earn less stars if you complete the level). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missing stars on a level? Replay it to increase your rewards.  <br> <br>Original soundtrack by <strong>Malin Eriksson</strong>. <br>    <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/b69f3e821abf8d027be770fffeef2699.webp?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/2f5d70c1a79eff5d1564b1be19ae3c82.poster.avif?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/2f5d70c1a79eff5d1564b1be19ae3c82.webm?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/2f5d70c1a79eff5d1564b1be19ae3c82.mp4?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>TL;DR</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Footage, content and gameplay is subject to change at any time during the early access period.  <br> <br>During early access, content will be released continuously until the 3 acts that wraps up the main story are complete.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every act consists of 8 levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number of traps, weapons, enemy types and levels will increase with time. <br><br><u><strong>NOTE: Only 1 act is available so far in the early access.</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This will change further along development. <br><br>Also, there will be <strong>bugs</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hopefully, any such arising will be easy to find and get rid of with the help of the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/70970c2052064d4af0bd502490cd58c5.webp?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/d1d231264a1f43eb35a364c2906cf297.poster.avif?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/d1d231264a1f43eb35a364c2906cf297.webm?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/d1d231264a1f43eb35a364c2906cf297.mp4?t=1773410752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The base game will contain the first 3 acts which is the main story arc. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the acts, more traps, weapons and other items will be available. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through the campaign to unlock more game modes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 4 available heroes play very differently and complement eachother; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Waldis the wizard - expert in elemental damage, using mostly projectile weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Rolanda the paladin - employs buffs/debuffs and uses (mostly) melee weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Mike the soldier - uses instant-hit bullet weapons that require mana to reload. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Anthia the necromancer - inflicts spell damage instead of wielding weapons, also has access to minions. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696420/extras/a196b13d2934ba1da5ab3e8aaade3e13.webp?t=1773410752\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the official Discord server if you have any feedback about the game or the balancing thereof.</p>",
